org.tal.redstonechips.circuit
Class CircuitLibrary

java.lang.Object
  org.bukkit.plugin.PluginBase

          org.tal.redstonechips.circuit.CircuitLibrary
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.bukkit.command.CommandExecutor, org.bukkit.plugin.Plugin, CircuitIndex
public abstract class CircuitLibrary
extends org.bukkit.plugin.java.JavaPlugin
implements CircuitIndex

A JavaPlugin implementation for circuit libraries. Provides invisible inter-plugin communication with RedstoneChips and, by implementing the CircuitIndex interface provides a mechanism to register new circuit classes.

Author:
Tal Eisenberg
